camp oven
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:[mustering, bush work and exploration] a three-legged cast iron pot, with a flat lid, used in an open fire.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
